==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''kingfisher''' (''plural'' '''kingfishers''')
# Any of various [[bird]]s of the [[suborder]] ''[[Alcedines]]'', having a large head, short tail and brilliant [[colouration]]; they feed mostly on [[fish]].

